If CPR_FORCE_OPENSSL_BACKEND, CPR_FORCE_DARWINSSL_BACKEND, CPR_FORCE_MBEDTLS_BACKEND, and CPR_FORCE_WINSSL_BACKEND are set to to OFF, cpr will try to automatically detect the best available SSL backend (WinSSL - Windows, OpenSSL - Linux, DarwinSSL - Mac ...).

properties.name: HELPSTRING
